<lyrics>[V1]
 ʿạrf ạlly ybṣ fy mrậh
 ʿly̱ wsẖh wbʿdyn ynsạh
 lw mạsmʿtsẖ ṣwt ạllh hạtkwn zyh whạtnsy̱
 zy ạlbdẖrẗ ʿ ạlḥjr ạltẖmr mạlwsẖ ạ̉tẖr
 ḥty̱ lw nzl mṭr zy qlbk mạ yqsy̱
 tʿạlym ạllh gẖạlyẗ fy klạm ạlktạb
 ạḥfẓhạ wʿysẖ byhạ wạmlạ qlbk byhạ
 dh klạmh fy slṭạn ʿly̱ ḥyạẗ ạlạ̹nsạn
 qwẗ tgẖyyr lḥyạtk llmjd kmạn wkmạn
 ạftḥ qlbk lklạmh ṣdq ạ̹nh lyk ạ̹nt
 ymlạ qlbk bslạmẗ ttgẖyr ḥtẗ ḥtẗ</lyrics>
